Class PawnForwardMove

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.entities.Move

            • io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.moves.PawnForwardMove

  • public class PawnForwardMove
extends AbstractPawnMove
    A pawn can only move forward, by one square, except when it moves from its start position, in which case it may move forward by two squares. When reaching the last row, the pawn must promote into another piece.
